What is Prime Token?

What is Prime Token?

Prime Token is the official digital currency of Prime Worldwide, a firm established in 2022 that aims to combine the potency of multilevel marketing and cryptocurrency.

By merging the secure and efficient aspects of cryptocurrency with the proven business model of multilevel marketing, Prime Token intends to create a decentralized utility and tools that empowers users and reduces expenses for both buyers and sellers.

Prime Token is the official digital currency of Prime Worldwide, a firm established in 2022 that aims to combine the potency of multilevel marketing and cryptocurrency.

By merging the secure and efficient aspects of cryptocurrency with the proven business model of multilevel marketing, Prime Token intends to create a decentralized utility and tools that empowers users and reduces expenses for both buyers and sellers.

Token Burning

We permanently remove a certain number of Prime Tokens from the circulation.

  • Increased Scarcity and Value: This increases demand, leading to higher prices and greater liquidity

Meet The Team

Meet the individuals who provide comprehensive support to ensure smooth operations and exceptional membership experience

Alver Niño F. Reganit

President/CFO

Working President and CFO of Primeworldwide, with 18 years of experience as a professional networker and expertise in forex trading and crypto. He brings a wealth of experience and a strong network of clients and partners, leading the company towards continued growth and success.

Richard S. Llido

Vice Predisent/COO

With expertise in multilevel marketing and 5 years of experience in crypto. I possess strong leadership and management skills, focus on mentorship and connecting people, and ensure our company’s growth and success while delivering top-notch service to our clients.

John Gabriel Bajado

Marketing Director

Co-founder and marketing director of Prime WorldWide. With 13 years experience in multilevel marketing, founder of G2 Project online system, with expertise in forex and crypto trading. Mentor in personal growth and development. My passion is to develop strategic tools and provide guidance for the company’s direction.

Paul Villaruel

Operations Director

I bring a decade of experience in business operations and multilevel marketing, with expertise in sales coaching, customer experience, and operational excellence. My responsibilities include people management, manpower development, report consolidation, and implementing operating procedures.

Lloyd Anthony Nayona

Digital/Crypto Director

Crypto Director of Prime Worldwide. Founder & CEO of Cipher Capital. Tech visionary and Blockchain Developer with 7 years of experience. Startup investor and early blockchain pioneer in the Philippines.
